repo.name: Efreak Repo
repo.description:
This is a repository of apps to be used with F-Droid. Applications in this repository are official binaries built by the original application developers and released on the official github pages.
Included apps are FastHub (not listed in fdroid), FastHub-Re (also not listed, a more up-to-date fork of FastHub-Libre) and Hacki (updates are too fast for fdroid). More might be added eventually.
